messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别路由正确",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition stage: intent classification model/prompt"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块未能将用户关于“NBEV目标缺口”、“增加理财师”、“优化产品方案”的输入识别为营销规划意图，而是错误分类为“其他意图”，导致 stage 路由为 non_agent，后续规划流程被跳过。",
      "evidence": [
        "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name = '其他意图'",
        "extracted_output.turns[0].stage = 'non_agent'",
        "execution_trace.intent_recognition.evidence: actual_stage='non_agent', expected_stage='intent'",
        "reference_contract.expected_stage='intent'",
        "planning_output_probe: stage_match=false, actual_stage null"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE事件序列完整且协议完成",
      "fulfillment_status": "fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "",
      "evidence": [
        "event_summary.final_event='done', protocol_completed=true"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition stage"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图识别错误，实际 stage 为 non_agent，不符合预期 intent/planning 阶段。",
      "evidence": [
        "actual stage = 'non_agent', expected stage = 'intent'"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "code_refs": [
        "ext_repo:app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
        "ext_repo:app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py"
      ],
      "reason": "意图识别分类错误导致整个流程偏移"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块的意图分类模型或 prompt 未能将包含“NBEV目标缺口”、“增加理财师”、“优化产品方案”等关键词的输入正确归类为营销规划意图，而是误判为“其他意图”，从而触发了 non_agent 阶段路由，跳过了所有营销规划相关的 field_clarification、planning 等后续阶段，使系统无法产生预期规划输出。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "source": "extracted_output",
      "detail": "intent_name='其他意图', stage='non_agent', intent_code='4001'"
    },
    {
      "source": "execution_trace.intent_recognition",
      "detail": "actual_stage='non_agent' vs expected_stage='intent'"
    },
    {
      "source": "planning_output_probe",
      "detail": "stage_match=false, actual_stage null, card_count=0"
    },
    {
      "source": "judge_result.fulfillment_assessments",
      "detail": "意图识别路由正确 not_fulfilled, blocking=true"
    },
    {
      "source": "execution_stage_probe",
      "detail": "all stages succeeded but actual stage offset"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

